title: Mormon Tabernacle Choir - It's Christmas 1989
description:
Source: 1989 CD
-
Mormon Tabernacle Choir - It's Christmas 320cbr (Big Papi) 1989
-
By Richard 
This is one of the better Christmas albums as it has very traditional songs that fit the season so well. I had this as a cassette tape and could not find it in Australia and was very happy to see that it is still available in the US, so brought it without a moments hesitation as I just love it.
